Silk Road x402 is an anonymous marketplace on Solana where developers can list and sell private, legal software tools like bots and scripts without revealing their identities. It leverages the x402 protocol for instant, micropayment transactions in USDC, enabling seamless pay-per-download or pay-per-use without accounts or traditional gateways. The platform ensures secure delivery through Solana escrows, focusing on privacy and efficiency for both sellers and buyers.
